data.description: Step into modern luxury with this two-story gem, boasting three bedrooms and two and a half baths. The kitchen is a culinary masterpiece, adorned with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. Upstairs, new plush carpeting leads to three bedrooms and a versatile loft area. The owner's suite, a haven of relaxation, features a walk-in closet and a double vanity in the ensuite bathroom. This home seamlessly combines aesthetics and functionality, creating a space where contemporary living meets comfort. With its stylish finishes and practical layout, this residence is an invitation to embrace a lifestyle of modern sophistication.
